---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { SITE } from '../utils/seo';
const updated = '2026-07-01';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description={`${SITE.name} privacy policy.`}>
  <div class="container-prose py-12 prose-custom">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: {updated}</em></p>
    <p>This page explains what data {SITE.name} ("we", "us", "our") collects when you visit grindatlas.com and how we use it.</p>
    <h2>1. Data we collect</h2>
    <p><strong>Analytics:</strong> We use privacy-friendly analytics (Cloudflare Web Analytics) to count visits and page views. We do not set advertising cookies or track users across sites from this analytics provider.</p>
    <p><strong>Advertising:</strong> We use Google AdSense, a third-party advertising service. AdSense uses cookies to serve ads based on a user's prior visits to our site or other sites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its partners to serve ads based on the visit to our site and/or other sites on the Internet.</p>
    <h2>2. Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can accept or decline non-essential cookies using the banner on your first visit. Your choice is stored locally for one year. You can change your choice at any time by clearing your browser's local storage for this site.</p>
    <h2>3. Third-party services</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> — ad serving. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="noopener">Google's advertising policies</a>.</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong> — hosting and analytics. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a>.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>4. Your rights (EEA / UK / California)</h2>
    <p>If you are in the EEA, UK, or California, you have the right to access, correct, or delete personal data we hold about you. Email us at privacy@grindatlas.com to exercise these rights.</p>
    <h2>5. Children's privacy</h2>
    <p>This site is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>
    <h2>6. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. Material changes will be announced on the homepage.</p>
    <h2>7. Contact</h2>
    <p>Privacy questions: privacy@grindatlas.com</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
